how it work 

UpasthithiAI is the leading absence mitigation platform purpose-built to support large, distributed hourly workforces. 

We help organizations reduce absenteeism, streamline attendance management, and improve operational efficiency through policy-driven automation, 
real-time communication, and seamless integration with existing HRIS and timekeeping systems.

Our solution is specifically designed to manage hourly workforces ranging from 50 to over 1 million employees. 
With more than 300,000 active employees on the platform and over 1 million hourly employee records, 
UpasthithiAI is the largest and most scalable absence management solution of its kind.

We currently support over 500 companies, including industry leaders like C&S Grocers, Kraft Heinz, Coca-Cola, and Kohler,
with active operations in the United States, Canada, Mexico, the United Kingdom, and Australia.

Our tools eliminate manual point tracking and disciplinary processes by applying company policies at the moment of
absence—ensuring consistency, transparency, and accountability across the workforce. 
Clients typically see a return on investment of 10x, with reductions in absenteeism of up to 50%, overtime costs by 20%, and administrative workload by 66%.

With flexible, month-to-month service agreements, dedicated client support, and powerful 
dashboards for site-level and national visibility, UpasthithiAI empowers HR and operations teams to focus less on tracking and more on leading.

I currently serve as CEO of UpasthithiAI, the largest absence mitigation platform built for high-volume, hourly workforces. 
We help employers reduce absenteeism, cut overtime costs, and eliminate manual tracking through real-time, policy-driven automation. 
With over 500 clients—including Coca-Cola, Kraft Heinz, Kohler, 
and C&S Grocers—we support more than 300,000 active employees and manage over 1 million hourly employee records across the US, Canada, Mexico, the UK, and Australia. 
